::SkarBlaise::
    He thought to himself that this was an unusual valley.  He could not see 
anyway out and there were traps set all around.  The ones that hit him did 
little damage due to his size and brute strength.  However he came to the 
conclusion that whomever had set these traps knew he was coming and would 
probably be out to destroy him.  He was looking forward to it.
